iPhone:
* Signing in
* Jot detail view that shows comments and lets you comment and iPhone home screen grouping action to reveal actions to see that user's profile, all their jots on X subject, all jots on X subject
* Explore API calls
* User detail view
* In stream view, a side swipe that lets you unfollow a user completely and unfollow them on a subject
* Ability to write a jot, tag it in a subject, and then post it
